msgid "There's probably no point, this one didn't even do anything."
msgstr "應該沒有意義，這個一點用處都沒有。"

msgid "Nothing good can come out of stabbing every single plant you see."
msgstr "刺向妳所看到的每一株植物不會有什麼好處。"

msgid "(Is this plant eating something... or someone?)"
msgstr "(這株植物是在吃什麼東西...還是什麼人嗎？)"

msgid "(Should I really risk opening it?)"
msgstr "(我真的應該冒險打開它嗎？)"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "(Probably best not to...)"
msgstr "(最好不要...)"

msgid "(It's a person.)"
msgstr "(是個人。)"

msgid "(Are they... alright? They seem asleep.)"
msgstr "(他...還好嗎？看起來睡著了。)"

msgid "(Wait... that might be a demon. Maybe I'd better leave them alone.)"
msgstr "(等等...可能是惡魔。也許我最好別管他。)"

msgid "(Well... I'll look around while they wake up.)"
msgstr "(好吧...在他醒來前到處看看吧。)"

msgid "AH!"
msgstr "啊啊啊！"

msgid "...!?"
msgstr "...！？"

msgid "Ahh... AHH!"
msgstr "啊...啊啊啊！"

msgid "Get it off get it off get it off!!!"
msgstr "快拿開快拿開快拿開！！！"

msgid "Oh god... oh god... gaaaah!"
msgstr "天哪...天哪...啊啊啊！"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "...!"
msgstr "...！"

msgid "Did you just save me?!?"
msgstr "是妳救了我嗎？！？"

msgid "Everything was so dark and so gross, I thought I was gonna die for real this time!"
msgstr "一切都很黑暗又噁心，我以為我這次真的要死了！"

msgid "That gooey stuff was eating away at my skin, it's so itchy, uuugh I still feel it!!!"
msgstr "那黏黏的東西在侵蝕我的皮膚，好癢，噁~我還感覺得到！！！"

msgid "I don't want it to eat me!!!"
msgstr "我不想被它吃了！！！"

msgid "Oh god, I didn't plan to get digested today, this is NOT how I pictured my death!"
msgstr "天哪，我還沒準備好被消化掉，這不是我想像中的死狀！"

msgid "WHAT IS THIS PLACE?!?"
msgstr "這是什麼地方？！？"

msgid "Oh."
msgstr "喔。"

msgid "Hahaha no..."
msgstr "哈哈哈不會吧..."

msgid "We're in the fairy ring aren't we?!"
msgstr "我們不會就在妖精環裡吧？！"

msgid "Noooo! There's no way to get out of here!!"
msgstr "不~~！沒有辦法逃離這裡！！"

msgid "This is it. WE'RE DEAD!"
msgstr "結束了。我們死定了！"

msgid "I might as well go back in the plant, at least it will be faster."
msgstr "我寧願回到植物裡，至少這樣更快。"

msgid "Nooo I don't want it to end this way!!!"
msgstr "不~~我不想要就這樣結束！！！"

msgid "Hey."
msgstr "嘿。"

msgid "...?"
msgstr "...？"

msgid "Cut it off."
msgstr "停下來。(Cut it off.)"

msgid "...W-what...?"
msgstr "...什-什麼...？"

msgid "I said: cut it off."
msgstr "我說：停下來。"

msgid "Ah, s-sorry..."
msgstr "啊，抱歉..."

msgid "(Is that supposed to be... a joke?)"
msgstr "(這應該是...笑話嗎？)"

msgid "You know, I'm actually okay with dying."
msgstr "妳知道嗎，我其實對死亡沒什麼意見。"

msgid "But I feel like being eaten alive isn't really the way to go, you know?"
msgstr "但是我覺得被生吞不是理想的死法，妳懂嗎？"

msgid "I see... I guess so."
msgstr "我懂...應該吧。"

msgid "My name's Aoi."
msgstr "我的名字是葵。"

msgid "...I see."
msgstr "...我知道了。"

msgid "Lacie."
msgstr "萊西。"

msgid "Hehe... Were you trapped in one of those things too?"
msgstr "嘻嘻...妳之前也被困在裡面嗎？"

msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "是啊。"

msgid "How'd you get out?"
msgstr "妳是怎麼逃出來的？"

msgid "${item:ch1.scissors}."
msgstr "${item:ch1.scissors}。"

msgid "Whoa."
msgstr "哇。"

msgid "If I get out of here I'll always carry scissors on me!"
msgstr "如果能逃出去的話我一定要隨身攜帶剪刀！"

msgid "I promise you-"
msgstr "我保證-"

msgid "No!"
msgstr "不！"

msgid "I SWEAR to you."
msgstr "我向妳*發誓*。"

msgid "O-okay..."
msgstr "好-好吧..."

msgid "(What am I supposed to say to that...?)"
msgstr "(我該說些什麼呢...？)"

msgid "So um..."
msgstr "嗯所以..."

msgid "H-how do we get out..."
msgstr "我-我們要怎麼逃出去..."

msgid "I don't know."
msgstr "我不知道。"

msgid "WE'RE ABSOLUTELY NEVER GETTING OUT WHAT ARE WE GOING TO DO!?!"
msgstr "我們永遠都出不去，我們該怎麼辦！？！"

msgid "Should I go back and get eaten by that plant instead?"
msgstr "我該回去讓植物吃了我嗎？"

msgid "That might actually be better than losing my mind as I walk endlessly through this hellish place..."
msgstr "這可能比在這鬼地方一步步失去理智還好..."

msgid "Can you imagine it???"
msgstr "妳能夠想像嗎？？？"

msgid "We would go insane!"
msgstr "我們會發瘋！"

msgid "I hear the fairy ring slowly digests you, even if you're not caught in a plant."
msgstr "聽說妖精環會慢慢消化掉妳，就算妳沒有被植物困住。"

msgid "Eventually the skin on our feet will start chipping away from walking through this visceral floor."
msgstr "我們的腳最終會在這內臟般的地上被逐漸削掉。"

msgid "Then we'll start crawling, when our feet no longer work, hoping for the sweet release of death."
msgstr "然後在我們的腳廢掉之後開始爬行，希望能夠得到死亡帶來的解脫。"

msgid "We might even wind up eating each other..."
msgstr "我們還有可能吃掉對方..."

msgid "Aoi."
msgstr "葵。"

msgid "R-right..."
msgstr "喔-對..."

msgid "Sorry."
msgstr "抱歉。"

msgid "I'll look around first."
msgstr "我先四處看看。"

msgid "I want to take another look at the next room."
msgstr "我想要看看另一個房間。"

msgid "I haven't even left this room yet."
msgstr "我根本就還沒有離開這個房間。"

msgid "OKAY!"
msgstr "好吧！"

msgid "Can I follow you?"
msgstr "我可以跟著妳嗎？"

msgid "No thank you."
msgstr "不用，謝了。"

msgid "Y-you'll leave me alone?!"
msgstr "妳-妳要把我丟在這裡嗎？！"

msgid "Please let me come with you, I promise I'll be useful!"
msgstr "拜託讓我跟著妳，我保證我會很有用！"

msgid "...uh..."
msgstr "...呃..."

msgid "PLEASE!!!"
msgstr "拜託！！！"

msgid "Okay... okay."
msgstr "好啦...好啦。"

msgid "(It's probably a bad idea, but...)"
msgstr "(這大概是個壞主意，但是...)"

msgid "(This... boy... or girl? They don't seem dangerous.)"
msgstr "(這個...男孩...還是女孩？看起來不危險。)"

msgid "(Maybe it's best not to be alone in this place.)"
msgstr "(也許在這個地方獨自行動不是最好的選擇。)"

msgid "...Yes, I don't see why not."
msgstr "...好吧，應該沒差。"

msgid "Yay!"
msgstr "好耶！"

msgid "I promise I'll be useful!"
msgstr "我保證我會很有用！"

msgid "Sure. Pleased to make your acquaintance."
msgstr "當然了。很高興認識妳。"

msgid "(I wonder if this girl... or boy... can help me with my problem.)"
msgstr "(不曉得這女孩...還是男孩...可不可以幫忙解決我的問題。)"

msgid "(Were they... melting? They might be a spirit or something...)"
msgstr "(他是在...融化嗎？他可能是精靈之類的...)"

msgid "(For now, let's focus on getting out of this place.)"
msgstr "(現在，專心想著怎麼離開這裡。)"

msgid "There's no one else to rescue in there."
msgstr "裡面沒有人要救了。"

msgid "It probably learned its lesson, I think."
msgstr "我想它應該學乖了。"

msgid "Various plants, similar to the one that caught you."
msgstr "各種植物，像是捉住我的那種。"

msgid "This one seems to be digesting something..."
msgstr "它看起來在消化什麼東西..."

msgid "The thing that almost ate Aoi. It's wide open."
msgstr "幾乎要吃掉葵的東西。打開了。"

msgid "The plant I was trapped in."
msgstr "剛剛困住我的植物。"

msgid "It's not nice in there."
msgstr "裡面不太舒服。"

msgid "Does this even classify as a plant?"
msgstr "這還能算是植物嗎？"

msgid "Not sure..."
msgstr "不確定..."

msgid "It kinda looks like one."
msgstr "看起來像是。"
